data.description: Welcome to Swan Lane. A Spacious Split Entry with 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, & 2 car attached garage awaits a new owner. Extra large deck with a Beachy Vibe and remote control awning. Main floor- 2 bedrooms, kitchen/dining room, living room, bathroom & foyer. Lower level-Spacious family room with gas fireplace, office nook, 2 bedrooms, laundry/utility room, storage area, & bathroom. Updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances (Refrigerator, stove, microwave, dishwasher). This home has NEW siding, NEW roof, NEW patio door and NEW windows (except 2 kitchen crank outs and 3 windows in basement). Interior painted, built-in office nook and added cubbies and storage. Fire pit. Play set. This property has a lot to offer. MUST SEE to appreciate!!  Call and schedule your showing today  :)
